style=\"color: rgb(221, 57, 46);\">//花舞人间</span><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">西南首座花城，</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">也许你看过各种各样的城楼，大多是土墙坚固威严，但你何时见过这样布满鲜花的城楼，“故事的小黄花，从出生那年就飘着”，黄金菊，似菊非秋菊，夏至绽芳华！</span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hupovip.cn//ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20190604/1559633041874096862.jpg?x-oss-process=style/image-zip\" title=\"321559626562_\" alt=\"321559626562_.jpg\" style=\"width: 400px; white-space: normal;\"/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hupovip.cn//ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20190604/1559633459068047969.jpg?x-oss-process=style/image-zip\" title=\"141559626438_.pic_hd\" alt=\"141559626438_.pic_hd.jpg\" style=\"width: 400px;\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hupovip.cn//ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20190604/1559633493829093294.jpg?x-oss-process=style/image-zip\" title=\"171559626439_.pic_hd\" alt=\"171559626439_.pic_hd.jpg\" style=\"width: 400px;\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hupovip.cn/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180730/1532935046040021412.png?x-oss-process=image/format,jpg/quality,q_60/resize,w_750\" title=\"交通路线\" alt=\"交通路线.png\" style=\"width: 1579px; white-space: normal;\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 57, 46);\">自驾</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">导航<span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">成都市新津县岷江大道666号重归亚特兰蒂斯欢乐世界</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hupovip.cn/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180619/1529378678658012424.png?x-oss-process=image/format,jpg/quality,q_60/resize,w_750\" title=\"温馨提示\" alt=\"温馨提示.png\"/><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">1、为您的安全起见，乐园内不得穿轮滑鞋，不得使用滑板、骑自行车及携带宠物进入，园内不设置看管，请提前做好安置。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">2、客服咨询：请直接点击左下角客服图标进行咨询。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p>',
